<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well, sure, but that=C2=A0<em>is=C2=A0</em>a f=
ight about AI safety. It=E2=80=99s just a=C2=A0<em>metaphorical=C2=A0</em>f=
ight about AI safety. I am sorry, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/33523803.281430/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9=
