ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
 rogue trading</a> and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
lick/33523803.281430/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbG=
VzLzIwMTktMDgtMzAvd2F0Y2gtb3V0LWZvci10aGUtbW9uZXktbWFjaGluZT9jbXBpZD1CQkQxM=
